Columns: 30;
                                                  ruled lines: 15;
                                                  written lines: 15; Uniform layout. Ruling by hard point,
membrane by membrane.Visible pricking. Partial borders between columns, with floral decorations, in colours.  Three tagin on שעטנזגץ. In the first nine columns the letters בדהחיק provided with only one tag. The names of the sons of Haman arranged in 11 lines, in accordance with the rule. Wooden roller (315mm high).
